1. *Temperatura* u sobi je previsoka. (The *temperature* in the room is too high.)
2. Kolika je dnevna *temperatura* danas? (What is the daily *temperature* today?)
3. Lekar mi je rekao da merim *temperaturu* redovno. (The doctor told me to measure my *temperature* regularly.)
4. Jutarnja *temperatura* je bila ispod nule. (The morning *temperature* was below zero.)
5. Treba da proverimo *temperaturu* hrane pre nego što je serviramo. (We need to check the *temperature* of the food before serving it.)
6. *Temperatura* koju osećam je groznica. (The *temperature* I'm feeling is a fever.)
7. *Temperatura* se spustila tokom noći. (The *temperature* dropped during the night.)
8. Pogledaj na *termometru*, koja je *temperatura*? (Look at the *thermometer*, what's the *temperature*?)
9. Kada mi je loše, često imam visoku *temperaturu*. (When I feel sick, I often have a high *temperature*.)
10. Zbog visoke *temperature*, odlučili smo da ne idemo na izlet. (Because of the high *temperature*, we decided not to go on a trip.)